          "Lily’s brother Chris gets kidnapped pretty much straight away by the evil Minotaur King off the back of a casual ‘I wish my brother would be taken away’ wish by Lily. This added a layer of guilt that Lily experiences throughout the rest of the story, which actually makes it slightly more nuanced than the usual kidnapping story."
